{"tid":508303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大專生月入中位數　20年跌1成","createTime":"2017-12-24T06:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T13:00:07.000Z","uid":47714,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2d234601bc534e396a2cbcbd1c15b52c3e018d36","tid":508303,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T06:23:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171213/57576856\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171213%2F57576856&d=JZ0Zg%2FVp23Hx9Oz8XqdEQjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=33f5e0a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171213%2F57576856&h=e0dee436\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171213/57576856</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171213/large/1513157338_3a55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171213%2Flarge%2F1513157338_3a55.jpg&h=fac7ee9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n分析政府統計處1996年至2016年的綜合住戶統計調查數據，並由1967年至2016年以每5年為一個世代，比較不同年代大專學歷勞工的收入差異及向上流動能力。數據顯示，從事低技術職位的大專學歷勞工從1996年8.69萬人，增長至2016年13.05萬人，升幅逾五成。惟去年擔任高技術職位的大專學歷人士只有55.3%，20年間跌幅近一成。<br />\n<br />\n收入方面，去年整體大專學歷勞工的收入中位數約1.75萬元，較1996年約1.93萬元減少9.2%，當中收入最高的一成大專學歷勞工的跌幅更達10.2%，反映大專學歷人士的整體收入持續下跌。"},{"pid":"1a15f6a6164d5fe063ad40defe067a866449d411","tid":508303,"uid":3122,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T06:30:14.000Z","msg":"當年尖子"},{"pid":"62115dd08f8ea98f11b7122b09399a579c4f75b8","tid":508303,"uid":49830,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T08:01:32.000Z","msg":"恆大又叫大學，教大又叫大學<br />\n心照la"},{"pid":"42895bc6b9012453332bc11d44ed46b217a39b43","tid":508303,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T08:02:52.000Z","msg":"不如講吓呢廿年嚟大學生增加咗幾多人先啦"},{"pid":"42992b36730ab40428519baeea7d8c9d2392a5e9","tid":508303,"uid":35815,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T08:26:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5995a07638a2a943c0cf27436b05756c50070161","tid":508303,"uid":2959,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T08:30:44.000Z","msg":"廿年前已經有hd asso？"},{"pid":"6e415930e8f51afb4efc0981c204a224b803a624","tid":508303,"uid":1790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T08:39:29.000Z","msg":"1萬9千3<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2579a2416effa2dc1cb289144a7f112ad20459c","tid":508303,"uid":56015,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T08:49:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如講吓呢廿年嚟大學生增加咗幾多人先啦</blockquote><br />\n多咗人又點？就算多咗堆原本上唔到大學嘅人都好，原本都上到嗰班正常嚟講，呢廿年人工唔會升嘅咩？照正路拉上補下唔至於跌啩？咁都跌，不如話呢廿年經濟及唔上97前啦"},{"pid":"8b3ff1a859ffd669a17ebfc454292e52fdcdef54","tid":508303,"uid":36857,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T08:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不如講吓呢廿年嚟大學生增加咗幾多人先啦</blockquote><br />\n多咗人又點？就算多咗堆原本上唔到大學嘅人都好，原本都上到嗰班正常嚟講，呢廿年人工唔會升嘅咩？照正路拉上補下唔至於跌啩？咁都跌，不如話呢廿年經濟及唔上97前啦</blockquote><br />\n今日嘅所謂大專生唔知有無當年中五程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當年中三做嘅職位，而家都要大專生啦"},{"pid":"f0b23aa4ec5f0dfee8c5e8cccf33059c3ff81803","tid":508303,"uid":36857,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T08:54:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>恆大又叫大學，教大又叫大學<br />\n心照la</blockquote><br />\n能大都叫大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果有日新聞同你講今日能大/恆大都有廿年前大學生嘅人工你仲驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67b3116523d7d2b30cb7de19edc260710928c74","tid":508303,"uid":36049,"like":